			<title>Document -Intersections: On-line Barriers to Oral Cultures and Parallels with Accessibility Barriers</title>
			<link>https://culturall1.idrc.ocadu.ca/index.php?option=com_content__view=article__id=54__catid=19__Itemid=53</link>
			<description><![CDATA[<p align="left">&nbsp;The Intersections document is the end result of the Intersections discussion series in which member of the Debajehmujig theatre troupe and the Adaptive Technology Resource Centre explored the similarities and differences&nbsp;between online barriers to access for people who live in oral cultures and people with disabilities.</p><p align="left"><a href="https://culturall1.idrc.ocadu.ca/other/intersection_report/">http://culturall.atrc.utoronto.ca/other/intersection_report/</a></p>]]></description>
