			<title>Event - Intersection Discussion Series - Face-to-Face Meeting (1 December 2006)</title>
			<link>https://culturall1.idrc.ocadu.ca/index.php?option=com_content__view=article__id=48__catid=19__Itemid=53</link>
			<description><![CDATA[<p align="left">The interesection discussions wrap-up with a face-to-face discussion during the Culturall Toronto Summit. Five members of Debaj and one person from the ATRC were involved in this wide ranging discussion that touched on gender specific knowledge, the use of Ojibway syllabics, how new words&nbsp;come into usage, storytelling and localization of stories.</p>]]></description>
