			<title>Event - Intersection Discussion Series - Face-to-Face Meeting (21 September 2006)</title>
			<link>https://culturall1.idrc.ocadu.ca/index.php?option=com_content__view=article__id=46__catid=19__Itemid=53</link>
			<description><![CDATA[<p align="left">In September 2006, Jan Richards and Heidi Hazelton, both&nbsp;of the ATRC, travelled to Wikwemikong, Ontario to meet members of Debajehmujig and begin the Intersections discussion series. The purpose of this conversation was to explore the similar (and different) barriers that exist to online participation&nbsp;for people living within oral cultures and for people with disabilities.</p>]]></description>
